{"tid":480575,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國人夫鍾情性愛機械人 妻：無出軌就得","createTime":"2017-11-26T09:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T10:13:03.000Z","uid":28366,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"29295801691158c8b9571c6250830e6a1b5d41ac","tid":480575,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:53:13.000Z","msg":"美國一名人夫鍾情性愛機械人，每周會與「她」進行四次性行為，更坦言自己若要在性愛機械人及妻子二選一，他會不知道如何選擇，但他的妻子竟欣然接受。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/11/20171125_pl_%E6%80%A7%E6%84%9B%E5%A8%83%E5%A8%83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F11%2F20171125_pl_%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%25A8%2583%25E5%25A8%2583.jpg&h=f564ec87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n58歲來自喬治亞州亞特蘭大的占士（James）將於美國第四頻道紀錄片「性愛機械人來臨」（The Sex Robots are Coming）分享自己與性愛機械人的經驗。占士有一名已結婚36年的妻子蒂恩（Tine），蒂恩早年因為要照顧媽媽，沒有時間陪伴他，為此占士花了2000英鎊<br />\n（約2萬港元）購買了性愛機械人「April」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/11/20171125_pl_%E6%80%A7%E6%84%9B%E5%A8%83%E5%A8%83_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F11%2F20171125_pl_%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%25A8%2583%25E5%25A8%2583_2.jpg&h=362063b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n占士每周會與「April」進行四次性行為，他形容「就如與一個真正的女人發生性行為一般」，更對「April」有「深深的感覺」，堅稱「她」不僅僅是一個性玩具。他更會悉心照顧機械人，為「她」化妝，與「她」約會，更有途人並無發現「她」不是一個活生生的人。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/11/20171125_pl_%E6%80%A7%E6%84%9B%E5%A8%83%E5%A8%83_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F11%2F20171125_pl_%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%25A8%2583%25E5%25A8%2583_3.jpg&h=fa8a6327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對著丈夫的喜好，蒂恩指：「我曾經為此感到不安，但隨時時間的流逝而變好了。」她又補充，「他大可以出去找別人（進行性行為），但他並無這樣做，他是真誠對待我的。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/11/20171125_pl_%E6%80%A7%E6%84%9B%E5%A8%83%E5%A8%83_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F11%2F20171125_pl_%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%25A8%2583%25E5%25A8%2583_4.jpg&h=f04f6a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n性愛機械人始終都需要更換，占士已經物色了一個價值8000英鎊（約8萬港元）的性愛機械人「Harmony」，該機械人將在未來幾個月內上市發售。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=zqM4iUZ1wkA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D1%26v%3DzqM4iUZ1wkA&d=D8gLfpKWQ00stTAtrJcZvZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=5692d87f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=zqM4iUZ1wkA</a>"},{"pid":"4b5e2ee3344b3b8af46427ef49bbd69fb70d22aa","tid":480575,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}